<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Tree Donation Certification</title>
  <style>
    body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        text-align: center;
       
        color: #495057;
        margin: 20px;
    }

    .certificate {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1476297816471-97713c4d237c?q=80&w=869&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D'); /* Path to your image */
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
    }

    h1 {
        color: #28a745;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 24px;
    }

    h2 {
        color: #007bff;
        font-size: 20px;
    }

    h3 {
        color: #e44d26;
        font-size: 18px;
    }

    p {
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .donor-name {
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #e44d26;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .donation-details {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .thank-you {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #007bff;
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .issued-on {
        color: #6c757d;
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: 14px;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="certificate">
      <h1>Tree Donation Certification</h1>
      <p>This is to proudly certify that</p>
      <div class="donor-name"><%= user.name %></div>
      <p>has made a generous contribution of</p>
      <div class="donation-details">
          <h3>$<%= user.amount %></h3>
          <p>for planting</p>
          <h3><%= user.noOfTrees %> trees</h3>
      </div>
      <p>and has become a valued contributor to environmental sustainability.</p>
      <p class="thank-you">Thank you for your commitment to making the world a greener place!</p>
      <p class="issued-on">Certificate issued on <span style="color: #e74c3c;"><%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %></span></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>